<h2>Epic SmartLinks That Save the Most Time</h2>

<p>SmartLinks auto-populate data from the chart. These are the highest-value SmartLinks for ICU nurses:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>SmartLink</th><th>What It Pulls</th><th>Use Case</th></tr>
